{
  "name": "RPlog_Chanti_at_a_swoop_race",
  "title": "Cold Business at the Marin Mountain Races",
  "summary": "At a freezing swoop race at the Marin Mountain Resort on Caspar, the Republic pilot Johanna grudgingly meets the cold, manipulative ex-Imperial warlord Zeak Oppenhiemer to discuss a clandestine arms deal, haggling over a quarter-million-credit price per piece while loathing the snow and his company. Zeak drapes his heated Imperial coat over her and steers them into a heated spectator tent, where the watchful Lady Athena, idly browsing Coruscant fashion, observes the pair and recognizes Zeak's COMPNOR pin. After Johanna asserts she is his equal and not his lackey, then storms off into the cold, Athena strikes up a guarded, fencing conversation with Zeak, hinting at her own ties to the Bureau of Operations and coolly declining to be impressed by the Empire before turning back to her datapad.",
